WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:15:59.376 --> 00:16:00.766 A:middle
bit about the feedforward that

00:16:00.766 --> 00:16:01.946 A:middle
we're going to have we should

00:16:01.946 --> 00:16:03.486 A:middle
try this out on a device as

00:16:03.486 --> 00:16:03.806 A:middle
well.

00:16:04.426 --> 00:16:05.946 A:middle
So again, I know this seems

00:16:05.946 --> 00:16:07.566 A:middle
really simple for a button, but

00:16:07.916 --> 00:16:09.866 A:middle
this is very important for

00:16:09.866 --> 00:16:14.036 A:middle
scroll, pinch, paging, a lot of

00:16:14.036 --> 00:16:14.976 A:middle
touch interactions.

00:16:20.046 --> 00:16:20.846 A:middle
Finally, we should think about

00:16:20.846 --> 00:16:23.476 A:middle
how to apply feedback after I

00:16:23.476 --> 00:16:24.826 A:middle
have lifted my finger up off of

00:16:24.826 --> 00:16:25.336 A:middle
this button.

00:16:25.926 --> 00:16:27.386 A:middle
For a physical button it's going

00:16:27.386 --> 00:16:28.966 A:middle
to return to its original state.

00:16:29.336 --> 00:16:32.266 A:middle
For our onscreen button we're

00:16:32.266 --> 00:16:33.866 A:middle
going to have lifted our finger

00:16:34.216 --> 00:16:34.946 A:middle
off the screen.

00:16:36.596 --> 00:16:38.496 A:middle
This is of course the realm of

00:16:39.276 --> 00:16:41.726 A:middle
classic feedback that most of

00:16:41.726 --> 00:16:42.466 A:middle
you are familiar with.

00:16:43.106 --> 00:16:44.466 A:middle
But the thing I want to point

00:16:44.466 --> 00:16:45.806 A:middle
out here is that we can be

00:16:45.806 --> 00:16:47.896 A:middle
thinking about feedback both for

00:16:47.896 --> 00:16:50.456 A:middle
the button itself and the

00:16:50.456 --> 00:16:52.526 A:middle
action, the result that is

00:16:52.526 --> 00:16:54.296 A:middle
happening, and we can think

00:16:54.296 --> 00:16:55.856 A:middle
about how to connect the two so

00:16:55.856 --> 00:16:57.696 A:middle
people understand what has

00:16:57.696 --> 00:16:58.116 A:middle
happened.

